text: Saint Andrew is one of Dominica's 10 administrative parishes. ==Settlements== Marigot is its largest village, with 2,676 people.Commonwealth of Dominica, Population and Housing Census—2001. Roseau, Dominica: Central Statistical Office, Ministry of Finance and Planning, Kennedy Avenue, 2001. Other communities include: *Wesley *Woodford Hill *Calibishie *Hampstead *Bense *Dos D'Ane *Anse du Mé *Paix Bouche *Thibaud *Vieille Case (also known as Itassi) *Penville ==References== Category:Parishes of Dominica
title: Saint Andrew Parish, Dominica
